data.description: This house is move-in ready, and the pride of ownership shines through in every corner. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in the beautiful Avon Estates, this stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home exudes warmth and character. The living and dining room areas are flooded with natural lighting, creating an inviting entertainment area. With a room on the first floor closed off by French doors, it'll make the perfect office or study space! The primary bedroom features a spacious en-suite bathroom with spacious walk-in closet to match. There is plenty of backyard space to include a deck that's perfect for backyard parties in the summer and making smores in the winter. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers, this home offers easy access to all the amenities you need! HVAC system replaced last year.
